# Scientific Basis for Bombe-Inspired Logic in AI Hardware

## ğŸ”¬ 1. Background

Alan Turingâ€™s **Bombe** machine was a revolutionary mechanical device developed to reduce the **combinatorial possibilities** in cryptographic keys used by the German Enigma machine. The logic relied on **rule-based pruning** to eliminate invalid key configurations early in the process.

We adapt this concept in modern AI hardware, particularly in **ASICs (Application-Specific Integrated Circuits)** used in crypto-mining and AI inference engines.

